        <updateDate>2021-09-12T19:36:59Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Keep Food Containers Safe from PFAS Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the use of perfluoroalkyl or polyfluoroalkyl chemicals (commonly referred to as PFAS) in food contact substances. A food contact substance is a substance intended for use as a component of materials used in manufacturing, packing, packaging, transporting, or holding food if such use is not intended to have a technical effect in such food.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Keep Food Containers Safe from PFAS Act of 2019</title>
    <titles>
