      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act to deem any perfluoroalkyl or polyfluoroalkyl substance used as a food contact substance to be unsafe and therefore treated as adulterated under such Act, and for other purposes.</title>
